          <p class="samsung-cost-body">Found a lower price at another Winnipeg repair shop? We'll match it - so you don't overpay. No pressure. No hassle.</p>
          <a href="sms:2045009757?body=Hey%20Mobile%20Tech%20Lab!%20I%20want%20a%20better%20price%20on%20a%20repair!" class="samsung-price-match-btn">
